title: battlestar.galactica.s03e11.ws.xvid-WITH.COMMENTARY
description:
This is the ORENJi release of S03E11 of Battlestar Galactica, but has the commentary by executive producer Ronald D. Moore that is provided from the offical podcast (http://www.scifi.com/battlestar/downloads/podcast/season03/) for sound, as well as the original sound much softer.

There is only the one audio track, with the commentary, so if you haven\&#039;t watched this episode please download the original one.
